==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Surpass
<hw>Sur*pass"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Surpassed</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Surpassing</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[F.
<ets>surpasser</ets>; <ets>sur</ets> over + <ets>passer</ets> to pass.
See <er>Sur-</er>, and <er>Pass</er>.]</ety> <def>To go beyond in
anything good or bad; to perform (an activity) better than; to exceed;
to excel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>This would <qex>surpass</qex>⟦br⟧
Common revenge and interrupt his joy.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- To exceed; excel; outdo; outstrip.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Surpassable</ent>⟦br⟧
